===Noun===
{{en-noun|-|cryptologies}}

# The practice of analysing [[encode|encoded]] messages, in order to [[decode]] them.
# Secret or enigmatical language.
#: {{rfquotek|Johnson}}

====Usage notes====
An umbrella term for [[cryptography]] and [[cryptanalysis]]. Cryptology is the study of mathematical, linguistic, and other coding patterns and histories.

